    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Combination instruments featuring the hammer action of the piano with the plucking jacks of the harpsichord, developed in the early 18th century.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
